msgid "SLIC - Salient Language In Context"
msgstr "SLIC - Salient Language In Context"

msgid "This research software allows researchers to collect data about which features of language people pay attention to as they hear it in real time, and provides listeners with the ability to review their reactions and justify why they reacted."
msgstr "Dette forskningssoftware giver forskere mulighed for at indsamle data om, hvilke sproglige træk folk lægger mærke til, mens de hører dem i realtid, og giver lytterne mulighed for at gennemgå deres reaktioner og begrunde, hvorfor de reagerede."

msgid "If you are a researcher"
msgstr "Hvis du er forsker"

msgid "To use SLIC as a researcher you will need to register for an account. To register you will need an invitation code, which can be obtained from the system administrator."
msgstr "For at bruge SLIC som forsker skal du registrere dig for en konto. For at registrere dig skal du bruge en invitationskode, som kan fås fra systemadministratoren."

